story.text: More sights today. More walking around narrow streets settled and resettled in the 6th and 13th centuries. A bit more wine and cheese. And an evening with Parisians - first chatting in a circle among friends, then umph umph in a club below [https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pont_Alexandre-III the Pont Alexandre III]. It was the most solidly constructed club I have ever experienced. I sadly determined that at 29, I have reached an age where I no longer enjoy the revelry of a club. This was a good one in which to have that realization.
